The paper discusses defense strategies against modern Botnets, which are a major threat to computer security. The paper focuses on measures and activities that can be carried out to establish successful defense against Botnets. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses software engineering (cs.SE) and system and information theory (cs.SI) aspects of defense against Botnets. Additionally, the paper discusses distributed systems (cs.DC) as Botnets are networks of compromised computers.
